Skin 101 (the101clinic.com/dr-tanvi-komawar) — Website Summary
================================================================

Overview
- Dermatology and aesthetic clinic in Baner, Pune led by Dr. Tanvi Komawar Adgudwar.
- Brand promise centers on “Beauty Inside Out” and “Your Journey to Timeless Beauty Begins Here”.
- Pages highlighted in the navigation: Home, About Dr. Tanvi, multi-level Services catalog, Our Gallery, Blog, and Contact.

Primary Calls-to-Action
- “Book an Appointment” button links to the contact form.
- Repeated “Call: +91-7055101101” buttons (desktop + mobile headers).
- WhatsApp/JoinChat floating button configured for +91 20401 86876.

Service Catalog
- Skin Treatments: Chemical peels, Carbon facial, Hydrafacial, Managing acne & scars, Vampire facial, Vitiligo surgery, Ear lobe repair, Skin treatment hub page.
- Laser Treatments: Laser hair removal, Laser skin toning, Mole removal, Carbon/laser facials, Laser treatment for piles, Laser treatment overview page.
- Hair Treatments: Hair loss treatment, Hair regrowth treatment, dedicated hair treatment landing page.
- Extended links in the global menu also surface additional procedures (Hair Treatment, Skin Treatment, Laser Treatment, Ear Lobe Repair, Vitiligo Surgery, Hair re-growth, etc.) for both Dr. Tanvi and Dr. Shashank service lines.

Experience & Value Props
- Multiple hero sections reinforce expertise: “Discover the Art of Radiant Skin with Dr. Tanvi Adgudwar” and “Your trusted destination for comprehensive dermatology care.”
- Repeated reassurance copy stresses personalized plans, cutting-edge technology, and confidence-building results.
- Visual emphasis via large imagery blocks for each treatment category (skin, laser, hair).

Educational Content
- “Explore our blog” block promotes fresh articles such as:
  • From PRP to Exosomes: Modern Hair Loss Solutions That Actually Work
  • Scalp Care Secrets: How a Healthy Scalp Leads to Stronger, Shinier Hair
  • How Hormonal Changes Affect Your Skin and the Best Ways to Manage Breakouts

Contact & Location
- Clinic Address: Ganraj Chowk, 101 Clinic, 2nd floor Whispering Woods Building, opposite Gera Emerald City, Baner, Pune, Maharashtra 411045.
- Phone: +91-7055101101. Email: surgery101clinic@gmail.com.
- Embedded Google Maps iframe pinpoints the Baner location; visitor counter shows 5,354 visits.

Footer & Social Proof
- Footer reiterates the “About Skin 101” blurb plus social icons for Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, and YouTube.
- Quick links to both Dr. Tanvi and Dr. Shashank landing pages.
- Copyright notice: “Copyright © 2025. All rights reserved.”

Utility Behaviors
- Site disables text selection/context menu and auto-prefetches internal links.
- JoinChat widget plus Elementor-powered layout dominate the original page markup.

